text: Kutushevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Meleuzovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 490 as of 2010. There are 16 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Meleuz, 11 km from Karan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Kutushevo
